popt4jlib.MSSC1D

Class Cluster

  • java.lang.Object
    • popt4jlib.MSSC1D.Cluster

  • public class Cluster
extends java.lang.Object
    the Cluster class represents a set of integers that together belong to a cluster, and provides methods for presenting 1-order statistics about this set.

    Title: popt4jlib

    Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java
